### Favorite API Test Requests

### Base URL
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7000/api/favorite

### 1. Get all favorites with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10&sortBy=CreatedAt&sortOrder=desc
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Get favorites by user ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/1
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Get favorite by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/1
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Check if item is favorited
GET {{baseUrl}}/check/1/HOTEL/123
Content-Type: application/json

### 5. Create a new favorite
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": 1,
    "targetType": "HOTEL",
    "targetId": "123"
}

### 6. Toggle favorite (add if not exists, remove if exists)
POST {{baseUrl}}/toggle
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": 1,
    "targetType": "RESTAURANT",
    "targetId": "456"
}

### 7. Update favorite
PUT {{baseUrl}}/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": 1,
    "targetType": "HOTEL",
    "targetId": "789"
}

### 8. Delete favorite by ID
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/1
Content-Type: application/json

### 9. Remove favorite by user and target
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/user/1/HOTEL/123
Content-Type: application/json

### 10. Get filtered favorites by target type
GET {{baseUrl}}?targetType=HOTEL&pageNumber=1&pageSize=5
Content-Type: application/json

### 11. Get filtered favorites by user and target type
GET {{baseUrl}}?userId=1&targetType=RESTAURANT&pageNumber=1&pageSize=10
Content-Type: application/json
